column1: # MethodDescription: Precipitation measured using a Geonor T-200B rain gage. Average of 6 readings in the final minute prior to reporting.
# QualityControlLevelExplanation: Raw and unprocessed data and data products that have not undergone quality control.  Depending on the variable
column4: raw data may be available within seconds or minutes after the measurements have been made. Examples include real time precipitation

column1: # SourceDescription: Continuous monitoring data collected by the University of Utah as part of the GAMUT network of the NSF iUTAH EPSCoR project.
